32 SPAWNPOINTS

GOOD for training different guns. You can pick up guns from the ground.

TITLE: CSS Map - cs_dodgewar_b1
VERSION: Beta 1
AUTHOR: akMan
E-MAIL: cs_akman@yahoo.com 
WEBSITE: http://www.freewebtown.com/cs_akman/csshome.htm

FILENAME: cs_dodgewar_b1.bsp 
FILESIZE: 1167 kb 
DATE RELEASED: March 6th, 2007

CREDITS: akMan - Map Creator 

INSTALLATION: Extract all files to Steam\SteamApps\STEAM_USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\

DESCRIPTION: A small accuracy-training map with boxes as cover and guns on the ground. As you go further out from your base, you will be able to get better weapons.
34 Spawnpoints (recommended 20 players max.)
This is the first version. There may be places that needs improvement. You can send suggestions/comments to cs_akman@yahoo.com.

COMMENTS: 34 Players in this map might be too much. About 20 would be nice.
Good tactics will help in this map.
